metadata.name: ON THE LOW
metadata.description:
The digital edition of an acrylic, 24 x 24 irl painting.

Featuring a nude angel with large fluffy wings, long blonde hair, rosy pink cheeks, and three green eyes; crouching down, looking over her shoulder and taking a selfie. She wears clear, stripper heels and fishnets, and large gem rings on each finger. Her exposed nipple is pierced, her nails are painted red, there is a golden harp to her left and stars in the sky. 

The original physical painting will never be sold. This is the only way to possess this piece.
